	   <tr><td colspan=2>Hello all.  I'm playing a High Elf wizard who is currently 10th level (un-twinked).  Currently, all I have is cloth armor and a cracked staff.  I don't have the money to purchase any magical rings or such so it's very difficult to lvl without getting my A$$ handed to me several times during a session.  Even if I root, nuke, root, nuke, on orc cents my mana runs out and they slam me left and right.  So does anyone have any advise on where to hunt to get good exp, money and items that will help me greatly at my level?  If so, please either post here or email me at camien_eq@yahoo.com.<br><br>Thanks in advance.<br><br>Camien<br>10 Lvl Wizard<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
