	   <tr><td colspan=2>Crushbone is your next step.<br><br>I am a L44 High Elf wiz... Trust me you won't like undead.  The Chess board in BB is all undead.<br><br>You really need L8 spells and more mana to survive long in CB.  Get some silver jade ear rings or if u got 20p or so get a Skull of Jhen Tra (spelling is not correct).  Ear rings are +5 mana each, skull is +20 mana.  Extra mana helps you level big time at your level.<br><br>Until then, you have L8 spells and extra mana, you can go to the cave at the entrance to CB.  Nice Exp there.  Get bind at orc lift.. saves effort when u gate or die.<br><br>Good luck & have fun<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
